    citation-agot-sansa-i:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Sansa I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Joffrey torments Mycah the butcher's boy near the Trident. Arya attacks Joffrey with a stick. Nymeria bites Joffrey's arm. Arya throws Lion's Tooth into the river. Sansa lies (or fails to tell the truth) before King Robert."
